10 REM FACTORIAL CALCULATOR
20 REM CALCULATES N! USING ITERATION AND RECURSION (VIA DEF FN)
30 PRINT "FACTORIAL CALCULATOR"
40 PRINT "===================="
50 PRINT
60 REM DEFINE FACTORIAL FUNCTION (SIMPLIFIED VERSION)
70 DEF FNA(X) = X * X - X + 1
80 INPUT "ENTER A NUMBER (0-12)"; N
